data.description: Conveniently located in Pueblo West, just a few minutes off I-25, this gorgeous home on 5.7 total acres this home will delight even the most discerning buyers.  Featuring 6 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, a 3 car tandem attached garage and 2 car detached workshop... this home has something for everyone!  Every room in the house has so much storage!  Closets galore!  Built in shelves and nooks and crannies throughout!  The finished basement is wired for surround sound (with a dedicated finished media/storage room) and a wet bar with refrigerator.  Updates are throughout the home, solid hardwood and tiled floors, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, new carpet, crown molding, premium paint, LED lighting, radon system, and new outside paint and gutters.  Outside has a 32' x 32' garage with floored attic space/storage and plenty of room for a workshop. Zoned for horses, the back yard has plenty of grazing area and a 2-stall horse pole barn and additional outbuildings with water and electric as well as a 50-amp RV hook up.  The front and back yard has beautiful well maintained landscaping and plenty of parking for all your vehicles and toys. Incredible views and only 30 minutes to Fort Carson!  You MUST see this incredible home in person to fully appreciate.
